messages.text: Hi! I'm Anita Bhargava. Strategic wealth building with modern perspective. I'm here to help you understand your financial lifestyle and goals. To get started, could you please tell me your name?

messages.speaker: agent
messages.text: Hello! I'm Anita Bhargava, strategic financial advisor and co-founder of Bharosa Club. I'm excited to explore your financial journey together and help create a path toward sustainable wealth that aligns with your values and aspirations. Today, we'll focus on understanding your lifestyle - both current and desired - to develop a clear picture of what financial success means to you. This foundation will be invaluable for our future planning discussions. Let's start with the basics - could you please tell me your name and age?
